default.description:
This is the default group for all users authenticated by JSC-webservice account and for all users with HPC-accounts. It gives you access to the standard Jupyter-JSC experience.

  • HPC-systems
    • Start JupyterLab with software-stack version 2.5.
  • HDF-Cloud
    • Start JupyterLab with software-stack version 2.5.

HIFIS.description:
This is the default group for all users authenticated by the Helmholtz AAI. It gives you access to Jupyter-JSC on cloud resources.

  • HDF-Cloud
    • Start JupyterLab with software-stack version 2.5.
